c: 48
v: 27
t: "Inene uAllâh Uza kuwufezekisa umbono wokwenyani Awawubonisa uMthunywa waKhe. Inene nina (maMuslim) niza kungena eMasjid al-Harâm, uAllâh Ethandile ngenene nangenyaniso, nichebe iintloko zenu, iinwele zenu ziphungulwe, ningoyiki bani. Yena (uAllâh) Wazi ebeningakwazi yaye Ucwangcise kwangaphambili kunoko uloyiso olukufuphi nolo (kungekudala)"